OOC: No, 2 missles out of one missle luancher.  If you have two, than you can 
2 from each of them.  Oh, sorry, didnt know what EMPs did. I'll take that 
back.

:::Sharpedge/Godfather/Hellbat/Sharpedge/Treadshot/Torca/Starscream:::

::He dodges the missles but gets hit by a charge andthe optic blasts.  he 
fires 2 missles at Hot Rod.  Godfather uses his jetpack to go over all the 
shots.  Staying in the air, he fired 15 shots from his pistol at Teltoli.  
Hellbat gets knocked out from the EMP.  Hearing what FZ said, Sharpedge opens 
up a comm to the Mafia::
Sharpedge: Mafia, do not for Mobster yet.  We must wait until they are 
weakened! Zardus' orders.
::Treadshot transforms to tank mode and lobbed 2 missles at Razor Claw. Torca 
hears Klant's words::
Torca: Thats alright, well wait here till you ARE ready.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

---------------------------------------------
::Starscream maneuvers out of the way of the fire ball, firing 25 shots from 
each of his 2 guns at Megaton::

--part1_3f.de39e4d.276a2af9_boundary
